plist_data.NSCameraUsageDescription: Mimip requests camera access to allow you to take progress photos as part of your health journey. Tracking visual progress alongside your BMR calculations can provide additional motivation and help visualize your health improvements over time.
plist_data.NSMicrophoneDeniedDescription: Without microphone access, you can still use all BMR calculation features and communicate with our AI chat through text input. All nutrition and exercise recommendations will remain available to help you on your health journey.
plist_data.NSMicrophoneUsageDescription: Mimip requests microphone access so you can verbally communicate with our AI health assistant. Voice interaction allows you to quickly ask questions about your BMR results, receive nutrition advice, and get exercise recommendations hands-free while working out.
plist_data.NSUserTrackingUsageDescription: At Mimip, your privacy is our top concern. We collect the text of your health information (personal, health, hobby-related) and progress data like update frequency and task completions. This data is used to show your progress visually and improve the app. We analyze patterns to optimize the interface, enhance notifications, and develop features for better goal achievement. We won't share your data without consent, except when required by law or for app security.
